-- Chile Steps Up Guard Against Real Estate Bubble, Mercurio Says
-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 2012-11-23T11:48:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-23/chile-steps-up-guard-against-real-estate-bubble-mercurio-says.html
Chile ’s central bank and Finance
Ministry created a working group to guard against a possible
bubble developing in the real estate market, El Mercurio
 reported today , citing the ministry’s International Finance
Coordinator Ignacio Briones.  The working group is part of the financial stability
council, which in addition to the ministry and central bank
includes the securities and pension regulators, the Santiago-
based newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Woods in Santiago at 
 rwoods13@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Goodman at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 